<h1>Product</h1>
<hr>
<p>eDakia product is much more than a application that run on top of any Android based mobile or tablet. It beautifully integrates with wireless Canon all-in-one-printer-scanner models. <em>It empowers any individual to send and receive posts just based on Mobile Numbers.</em></p>
<br>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> The whole system is <strong>Number based</strong> which makes it super easy to use by any literate or non-literate person.</p>
<br>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Anyone can directly E-Mail their letters, application, forms, requests, documents <strong>without english typing, computer proficiency and file attachment hassles.</strong></p>
<br>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Besides sending and receiving posts, eDakia acts like a <strong>Document Store</strong> for saving a copy of important documents like ID proofs, pan card, reports, agreements etc with an ease to access them anytime in case of urgency.</p>
<br>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Internally, it also creates a mobile number based E-Mail ID for registered users e.g. 981111xxxx@edakia.in. It helps user to receive <strong>email along with an SMS notification</strong> from anyone in the world.</p>
