<hr>
<h3>Send</h3>
<br>
<p><strong>Internet users: </strong> One can absolutely send files to non-internet users with the ease of sitting on your system.</p>
<p>Kindly follow the simple steps:</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Registration: Call <strong>011-30715555</strong> from your mobile phone and press 1 when prompted.</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Login at http://www.edakia.in with password provided to you by an SMS after successful registration.</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Click Send Post, enter recipient's mobile number and attach your file and click send.</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> You and Recipient will receive an SMS with Doc ID.
<br>
<br>
<p><strong>Non-Internet Users: </strong></p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Visit eDakia kendra with your hard copy documents.</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> Tell your and recipient's mobile number and keep the papers in the scanner.</p>
<p><strong> ➠</strong> With 2 clicks a copy of your document(s) is securely saved and shared by an SMS acknowledgement.</p> 
